OL,3,C'Desperate shortage' of care home beds
OL,4,Cwithin the next decade
OL,6,FA leading pressure group has warned of
OL,7,Fa "desperate shortage" of care home
OL,8,Fbeds in Wales over the next decade,
OL,9,Fwith the deficit reaching as many as
OL,10,F10,000.
OL,12,FThe research by business property
OL,13,Fadviser Christie & Co has been called
OL,14,F"alarming" by Care Forum Wales, who
OL,15,Frepresent care home owners across the
OL,16,Fcountry.
OL,18,FCartref Bryn Yr Eglwys nursing home in
OL,19,FPentrefoelas provides nursing or
OL,20,Fpersonal care for up to 30 residents
OL,21,Fat a time.
