OL,3,C'Desperate shortage' of care home beds
OL,4,Cwithin the next decade
OL,6,FIts manager, Meryl Welsby, has worked
OL,7,Fthere for more than 30 years and says
OL,8,Fthe challenges the home is facing are
OL,9,F"unprecedented".
OL,11,FShe told ITV Wales: "We've got huge
OL,12,Frecruitment problems. We've got the
OL,13,Fcontinuing changes to regulations but
OL,14,Fthe biggest issue we face is funding.
OL,16,F"It's extremely hard and if anyone
OL,17,Fthinks this is a profit-making
OL,18,Fbusiness then the hard work will put
OL,19,Fthem off.
