OL,3,C'Desperate shortage' of care home beds
OL,4,Cwithin the next decade
OL,6,F"You've got to be coming from a
OL,7,Fnursing or a care background and
OL,8,Fyou've got to have compassion, not
OL,9,Fonly for your staff but also your
OL,10,Fresidents.
OL,12,F40 elderly care homes in Wales have
OL,13,Fclosed and only four opened between
OL,14,F2020 and 2023, with no new homes
OL,15,Fopening in North Wales in that time.
OL,17,FGwynedd and Flintshire county councils
OL,18,Fhave drawn up plans to build new
OL,19,Ffacilities with around 100 beds, which
OL,20,Fhas an estimated cost of more than
OL,21,F#250,000 per bed.
