OL,3,C'Desperate shortage' of care home beds
OL,4,Cwithin the next decade
OL,6,FMario Kreft, the chair of Care Forum
OL,7,FWales, said: "The report from Christie
OL,8,F& Co paints a bleak picture and
OL,9,Fillustrates how the existing crisis is
OL,10,Fgoing to get even worse, creating a
OL,11,Fdouble whammy for our overstretched
OL,12,Fhospitals which have rows of
OL,13,Fambulances queuing outside and
OL,14,Fpatients on trolleys in corridors...
OL,16,F"The way care homes are funded in
OL,17,FWales is a total postcode lottery with
OL,18,F29 variations on a theme, with most of
OL,19,Fsocial care being commissioned by the
OL,20,F22 local authorities and seven health
OL,21,Fboards.
