OL,3,C'Desperate shortage' of care home beds
OL,4,Cwithin the next decade
OL,6,FHe continued: "The fundamental issue
OL,7,Fthreatening the viability of care
OL,8,Fhomes is the unrealistically low fees
OL,9,Fthat the vast majority of councils and
OL,10,Fhealth boards pay, fees that come
OL,11,Fnowhere near covering the true cost of
OL,12,Fproviding care."
OL,14,FMr Kreft said that it would "make a
OL,15,Flot more sense" to try to keep
OL,16,Fexisting care homes financially secure
OL,17,Finstead of relying on building enough
OL,18,Fnew ones to meet increasing demands
OL,19,Ffor social care.
