OL,3,C'Desperate shortage' of care home beds
OL,4,Cwithin the next decade
OL,6,FHe added: "The problems we have in
OL,7,Fsocial care lead to the pressures in
OL,8,Fthe NHS which lead of course then to
OL,9,Fextra costs being placed on the NHS
OL,10,Fwhich would largely be alleviated if
OL,11,Flocal authorities had a more
OL,12,Fenlightened approach to social care.
OL,14,F"The families of those people, who
OL,15,Fwill often be expected to make up the
OL,16,Fdifference, need to ask why and quite
OL,17,Ffrankly, it is a bridge too far.
OL,26,@nD@KOUvD@AOU
