OL,3,C'Desperate shortage' of care home beds
OL,4,Cwithin the next decade
OL,6,F"This is undoubtedly a stealth tax on
OL,7,Ffamilies and quite frankly, the people
OL,8,Fmaking these decisions in those
OL,9,Fauthorities should be utterly ashamed
OL,10,Fof themselves in the way they are
OL,11,Fbetraying vulnerable people including
OL,12,Fthose with profound dementia and their
OL,13,Ffamilies," Mr Kreft said.
OL,15,F"What this demonstrates is that there
OL,16,Fis an urgent need for us to look again
OL,17,Fat the way social care is funded.
