OL,3,C'Desperate shortage' of care home beds
OL,4,Cwithin the next decade
OL,6,F"We need a national approach to
OL,7,Feliminate this iniquitous postcode
OL,8,Flottery so that the people for whom we
OL,9,Fprovide care and our staff are treated
OL,10,Ffairly.
OL,12,F"This is too important to be left to
OL,13,Flocal authorities and health boards
OL,14,Falone ` it has to be driven by the
OL,15,FWelsh Government."
OL,17,FA Welsh Government spokesperson said
OL,18,Fthe commissioning of care home beds
OL,19,F"is a matter for local authorities and
OL,20,Fhealth boards."
